      "message": "\u003e But if the father container different versions of this library,\nfather -\u003e plugin - Sorry, was from my phone.\n\nMy point is, if we modify the gerrit-bsl-licence and rebuild the e.g. groovy-provider, will we have a away to know which version of this library was embedded in the groovy-provider?",
