      "writtenOn": "2026-07-01T19:58:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e But if the father container different versions of this library, would the version be the same?\n\nWhich _father_? This is a library included in other plugins: each one carries on its own built-time class and is completely independent. There\u0027s no father-child relationship anywhere: Gerrit plugins are fat-jars and include all their build-time dependencies.\n\n\u003e That\u0027s what I was trying to avoid.\n\u003e \n\u003e If we don\u0027t care about that, then this is fine.\n\nIf you see a problem, let\u0027s discuss it. If there are no problems, I don\u0027t see how more complexity can bring any value.",
